{
  "stem": "26672.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they live [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I found them, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't leave the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't leave the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was enlisted into the army, together with my friend [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we were not taken into the Anglo-Saxon-- there was Anglo-Saxons, quite a few of our boys in the 300, and the others were volunteers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we weren't taken, because we were-- I was mixed up with him, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't go particularly with the Anglo-Saxons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were enlisted into the [NON-ENGLISH], which is the [INAUDIBLE] brigade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first, as I said, we had a couple days off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were taken-- then we were taken on tours to get ourselves acclimatized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had a little bit of training in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were taken-- my camp was taken into a place called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is on the Gaza area, kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was also a-- what we call a [NON-ENGLISH], an observation post.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in the army, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Almost-- but not in that particular place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that place, we were in till we captured [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which was September, September, October in '48.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was one of the first who went to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, [LAUGHS], in that particular camp, in that particular place, called [NON-ENGLISH], first of all, they used to grill a lot of onions.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, yet, we had a group of Moroccans who joined our group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at night, each one had a gun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was only 10 bullets amongst the group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you only had one bullet, particularly, or two bullets, to put in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
